{"tid":2401681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"直播注射疫苗後暈到嘅女護士，至今仍然生死未卜","createTime":"2021-02-10T02:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T02:08:09.000Z","uid":222614,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee405b535de98ecb2341bf55eed89b115c23db24","tid":2401681,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"2020年12月17日，女護士 Tiffany Pontes Dover 現場直播接種 Pfizer Covid Vaccine 疫苗後 17 分鐘暈倒地上，此後一直未有公開露面，引發外界對她建康的揣測，有人甚至相信她已經離世。然而各大傳媒卻一致認為 Tiffany 當日暈倒與疫苗無關，並一度瘋狂出文 &quot;Debunk&quot;，可惜致今仍未悉除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n其實傳媒無論怎麼努力發文，也不夠一場記者會有效。公眾真正想要的，是 Tiffany 和她的醫生一齊出來再次面對公眾，解釋當日的情況到底與疫苗有沒有關連。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4g77fcyvBzw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4g77fcyvBzw&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=f38f18b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4g77fcyvBzw</a>"},{"pid":"610a4ce7bc232b5fe24d95e9ab45415754fd47e6","tid":2401681,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be386232c29ea2f44604ddaab40c76368e9eee0","tid":2401681,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T02:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339162e7023c1f9014552e7146605c6803fa8722","tid":2401681,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"push ...."},{"pid":"f34564e7124bec13865d5cd4987d60bd9cf77fb4","tid":2401681,"uid":222614,"like":2,"dislik